 the Olympic Village in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997139639, \"rank\": 2.858985283423354e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997244251198579, \"rank\": 0.00023173881062849876, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The announcement\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Explore\\\" feature\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"their location\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"profiles\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In ablog postshared Thursday, titled \\\"Grindr and Enhanced Privacy for Athletes at the ParisOlympics,\\\" the app explained that the decision to disable location services was made in an effort to protect queer Olympians from potentially being outed by individuals using Grindr.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}, {\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ablog\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Privacy\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"location services\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"queer Olympians\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If an athlete is not out or comes from a country where being LGBTQ+ is dangerous or illegal, using Grindr can put them at risk of being outed by curious individuals who may try to identify and expose them on the app,\\\" the company said.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"curious individuals\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being an LGBTQ+ athlete comes with its own unique set of challenges, especially for those who come from places that lack basic rights and protections for our community,\\\" Grindr said.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an LGBTQ+ athlete\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"its own unique set\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"basic rights\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"protections\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"our community\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's why we are taking the additional step of sending targeted safety resources and information, including weekly messages reminding users that they may face danger while using the app in the Olympic Village and sharing links to our multilingual safety resources.\\\"\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_2016_Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999830010894, \"rank\": 1.699869875100276e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_2016_Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_2016_Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the additional step\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"targeted safety resources\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"weekly messages\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"users\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"links\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"our multilingual safety resources\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to turning off the app's \\\"Explore\\\" and \\\"Roam\\\" features in the 