u shine.\\\"\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997139639, \"rank\": 2.858985283423354e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trailblazing LGBTQ+ athletes\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grindr, which launched in 2009, similarly disabled location features at the 2022 Winter Olympics in Beijing.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}, {\"begin\": 2814, \"end\": 2821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9987563898310811, \"rank\": 0.001244991810166308, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similarly disabled location features\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The security measures came after US news site The Daily Beastused the LGBTQ+ dating app to get dates with athletes at the Rio 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.7495172581349795, \"rank\": 0.33395551171887516, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 2949, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.699303996269037e-15, \"text\": \"2016 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The security measures\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"US news site\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"The Daily\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"the LGBTQ+ dating app\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"dates\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The article, which was later removed from the website, included details about individuals that could have identified them, such as their height, weight, nationality, and a description of their profile picture.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The article\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"their height\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"nationality\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"a description\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"their profile picture\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following widespread backlash, the Daily Beast removed the article and issued an apology.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3216, \"end\": 3221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dark_Beast\", \"score\": 0.926168306492037, \"rank\": 0.07971736129447826, \"text\": \"Beast\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dark_Beast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.or