story.\\\"\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"our story\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LGBTQ+ athletes were once again at risk at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ athletes\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3777}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3801}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the games, which took place in 2021 due to the Covid-19 pandemic, TikTok users had posted videos with the names and pictures of Olympians' Grindr profiles,Business Insiderpreviously reported.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3903, \"end\": 3909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1254681873487724e-40, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 3976, \"end\": 3982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grindr\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grindr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid-19 pandemic\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3948}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"Business\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toOutSports, the Paris 2024 Olympics will include more than 150 LGBTQ+ athletes competing in this year's games.\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\